<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Slack Mobile Preview ({{ timestamp }})</title>
  <!--
    Design Ref §4.2 — Galaxy S23+ font stack.
    Plan FR-03: Noto Sans KR (한글) + Roboto (영문) + Noto Color Emoji (이모지) + Roboto Mono (code).
    Samsung One UI는 시스템 폰트라 웹폰트 X — Noto Sans KR가 사실상 동등.
  -->
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans+KR:wght@400;700&family=Noto+Color+Emoji&family=Roboto:wght@400;700&family=Roboto+Mono&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    * { box-sizing: border-box; }
    html, body {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      background: #f4f4f4;
      /* Slack Android: body 약 15-16px. Noto Color Emoji는 fallback. */
      font-family: 'Noto Sans KR', 'Roboto', 'Noto Color Emoji', sans-serif;
      font-size: 15px;
      line-height: 1.45;
      color: #1d1c1d;
      -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
    }

    .slack-channel {
      background: #fff;
      padding: 12px 14px;
      min-height: 100vh;
    }
    .channel-header {
      font-size: 13px;
      color: #616061;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #e1e1e1;
      padding-bottom: 8px;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
    }
    .message {
      /* Slack mobile: preserves whitespace + wraps long words. */
      white-space: pre-wrap;
      word-break: break-word;
      overflow-wrap: anywhere;
    }
    pre.code-block {
      background: #f8f8f8;
      border: 1px solid #e1e1e1;
      border-radius: 4px;
      padding: 8px 10px;
      margin: 6px 0;
      font-family: 'Roboto Mono', 'Courier New', monospace;
      font-size: 13px;
      /* Slack code block: monospace, but Korean falls back to proportional. */
      white-space: pre;
      overflow-x: auto;
    }
    code.inline-code {
      background: #f8f8f8;
      border: 1px solid #e1e1e1;
      border-radius: 3px;
      padding: 1px 4px;
      font-family: 'Roboto Mono', monospace;
      font-size: 13px;
    }
    strong { font-weight: 700; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="slack-channel">
    <div class="channel-header"># 미증시지수 ▾</div>
    <div class="message">{{ content|safe }}</div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
